# Web project (Vercel or local). API_URL is server-only; users never see it.
# Production: set API_URL to your backend (e.g. https://api.your-domain.vercel.app)
# Local dev: if the API runs on port 4000, submission works without setting this (fallback).
# To use a different backend URL, set API_URL (e.g. http://localhost:4000):
# API_URL=http://localhost:4000
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your-key
